- This will run upto our max_so_far become >=n-1 i.e end point so after that we will return the answer (no. of jumps till now).
- There are two  ways of doing greedy like shown below : First one seems like more bfs type but both are actually implicit bfs ,idea is same incremnet the level and check in curr level the  max jump we can take  and when max > n-1 we will return the no .of levels  till now.
