The string holding all the vowels of the string(say, temp) will be iterated in reverse manner(j = temp.size() - 1) and whenever we will find a vowel in origginal stirng we will replace it with temp[j] and decrement j. This way we will replace all the vowels in reverse order. The code is attached for reference.

