4 Possible Cases are there that left and right Pointers are Pointing to:
**1.vowel and vowel** `[swap and l++ and r--]`
**2.vowel and non-vowel** `[find other vowel on right side . Decrease right pointer (r--) only]`
**3.non-vowel and vowe**l `[find other vowel on left side . Increase left pointer (l++) only]`
**4.non-vowel and non-vowel** `[no swap and l++ and r--](because want to swap vowels only)`
